Package dataStructure

Class DGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • dataStructure.DGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    graph, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    public class DGraph
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements graph
    This class a directional weighted graph. The class has a road-system or communication network in mind - and should support a large number of nodes (over 1,000,000). The implementation is based on HashMaps and the graph has two main Hashmaps the first is the Hshmap of nodes ,and the second is the hasmMap of Neighbore that has a Hashmap as value inside evry node that has edge as value .
